{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id8f14f49d-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s1643l"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1643l"},"text":"§ 1643l.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Determination of ownership of claims referred by district courts of the United States","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding any other provision of this chapter and only for purposes of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s6082"},"text":"section 6082 of this title","children":[],"tail":", a United State "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002073"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002073"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":"So in original. Probably should be “States”."}],"tail":" district court, for fact-finding purposes, may refer to the Commission, and the Commission may determine, questions of the amount and ownership of a claim by a United States national (as defined in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s6023"},"text":"section 6023 of this title","children":[],"tail":"), resulting from the confiscation of property by the Government of Cuba described in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s1643b/a"},"text":"section 1643b(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":", whether or not the United States national qualified as a national of the United States (as defined in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s1643a/1"},"text":"section 1643a(1) of this title","children":[],"tail":") at the time of the action by the Government of Cuba."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id8f14f49e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1950-03-10/ch54"},"text":"Mar. 10, 1950, ch. 54","children":[],"tail":", title V, § 